Design an infographic that highlights the impact of lifestyle choices on the development and management of type 2 diabetes.

The infographic should include the following:

The prevalence of type 2 diabetes globally, including statistics on the number of people affected and the projected increase in cases over the next decade.

The risk factors for type 2 diabetes, such as age, family history, obesity, lack of physical activity, and poor diet.

The impact of type 2 diabetes on health, including complications such as heart disease, kidney damage, nerve damage, and vision problems.

The importance of lifestyle modifications in preventing and managing type 2 diabetes, including tips on healthy eating, regular exercise, stress management, and quitting smoking.

The benefits of early detection and treatment, including the use of medications and regular monitoring of blood glucose levels.

Resources for people with type 2 diabetes, including support groups, education programs, and online resources.

The role of healthcare providers in managing type 2 diabetes, including the importance of regular check-ups, medication management, and coordination with other healthcare professionals.

The infographic should be visually engaging and easy to understand, with clear headings, colorful images, and concise text. It should provide a comprehensive overview of type 2 diabetes and encourage people to take steps to prevent and manage this common health condition.
